{"type": "article", "id": 26412, "title": "飞碟摇椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-05T07:08:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132502EO4ZHIuy1wB0bRt6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"medium-insert-active\">越来越多的家具开始结合科幻元素了，意大利设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.itoneoff.com/\">IT ONEOFF</a> 最近就推出了一款名为 UFO 的摇椅（名字倒也是挺形象的）。它的外壳由整块碳纤维制成，内部是手工制作的皮革座位，红黑款颇有科幻片中驾驶舱的感觉，你可以蜷缩在里面看上一本书或者是打个小盹儿。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132500b15rqzXsoEZe9I4A.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132500MguzVt1Dmw0GY8nk.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132501dznjhkx9bTucS6lr.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}